		</div>
		<div class="page-wrap text">
			<p>
				<strong><em>I'm skilled.</em></strong><br><br>
				From my research background, I've developed a good knowledge base of statistical tools and scientific research methods, including basic data analysis techniques along with ANOVA, regression techniques, cluster analysis, random forests, and data visualization. And with regards to statistical tools I'm proficient in R (including ggplot2), Python (including pandas), Matlab, and Excel (including pivot tables). <br><br>
